{
  "stem": "26699.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Early memories go to strolls through the town to the-- to famous gardens, public gardens, in this town, where great poets of Romania were composing their poems.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I still can visualize the house where I was born and we lived for about three or four years, and from where we moved into a different house on the main street of Iasi, which was quite an improvement.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "On Strada Bratianu, B-R-A-T-I-A-N-U.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Not far from my father's shop, just, let's say, ten minutes' walk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I do remember the marketplace, an open marketplace.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I do remember the hospital just across the road from my father's shop.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And actually, the house where the shop was accommodated the rest of our family upstairs, where my grandfather, my grandmother, were living there, and together with them some of my aunts and uncles.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was a big house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I do remember that it was a very big dining room, where the whole family was reunited on Shabbat evening, and with occasions of other holidays or birthdays.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In this time-- so I'm talking about the period before the Second World War-- a lot of people were spending their summer holiday at various spas which were not far from Iasi.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The whole area was so beautiful and so green, and the fresh air was everywhere, that at distances of about 50, 60, 80 kilometers around Iasi, there were famous spas with good food, good rest, and good mineral waters.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the rule was that the grandparents, they were taking the grandchildren there for the sole purpose to get them strong and fed, and feed them up to they couldn't eat anymore.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the greatest reward was when coming back after a month to put them on a scale, and to find out how much weight they gained.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
